Title: Clear Gasoline Locator
Description: Build an app that helps motorists find "clear" gasoline locations throughout the state of Oregon.

Title: Have a great idea?
Description: If you have an idea for a great app that needs a specific dataset from an Oregon agency or entity, please suggest a dataset!

Title: Bills signed by Governor
Description: Use this dataset and others for previous years to build an for an app that tracks Oregon bills signed by the Governor
